 prone to false positives (e.g. MSI Plessey)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For those barcode types false positives can be drastically reduced (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode128Configuration/initWithRegexFilter:minimumSizeScore:addAdditionalQuietZone:minimum1DQuietZoneSize:minimumNumberOfRequiredFramesWithEqualRecognitionResult:oneDConfirmationMode:gs1Handling:minimumTextLength:maximumTextLength:enableOneDBlurScanner:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithRegexFilter:minimumSizeScore:addAdditionalQuietZone:minimum1DQuietZoneSize:minimumNumberOfRequiredFramesWithEqualRecognitionResult:oneDConfirmationMode:gs1Handling:minimumTextLength:maximumTextLength:enableOneDBlurScanner:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"initWithRegexFilter:minimumSizeScore:addAdditionalQuietZone:minimum1DQuietZoneSize:minimumNumberOfRequiredFramesWithEqualRecognitionResult:oneDConfirmationMode:gs1Handling:minimumTextLength:maximumTextLength:enableOneDBlurScanner:","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbarcodeformatcode128configuration\/initwithregexfilter:minimumsizescore:addadditionalquietzone:minimum1dquietzonesize:minimumnumberofrequiredframeswithequalrecognitionresult:onedconfirmationmode:gs1handling:minimumtextlength:maximumtextlength:enableonedblu